name: Beginning
description:
This is where the adventurous journey of a cat named Charcoal and his goldfish friend begins. The world is so big for him to learn.
The fun of my work is to combine the art of mechanical writing with different things. both place and life You don't want to see the Great Wall of China with a dragon head and a machine. Or Stonehenge the robot?
The easter egg in this photo is the 35 cats in the picture. Let's find it all.
